== 評價 ==
2022年3月，《美麗心靈》在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]評選奧斯卡金像獎最佳影片前35名中，排名第29名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/pictures/best-picture-winners-ranked-from-worst-to-best/6|title=35 Best Picture Oscar Winners, Ranked From Worst to Best|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2022-03-22 |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-22 |archive-url=https://www.metacritic.com/pictures/best-picture-winners-ranked-from-worst-to-best/6|dead-url=no }}</ref>

